).

Female tergum 8 with slightly concave posterior margin (
Fig. 24
), sternum 8 with posterior margin forming obtuse lobe (
Fig. 23
). Females have two spine­like accessory sclerites (
Fig. 25
). Spermatheca forming two­three coils (
